    "The second group (16.8%) tested different iVR-related variables and the results were compared with several other groups.",
    "In most of the experiences, a pre-test was included to collect the demographic data of the users (i.e., age, gender, educational level, and previous experience with iVR).",
    "The data were used to evaluate whether any of the demographic factors conditioned subsequent performance.",
    "As that is a widespread and general practice, it was not analyzed in this review.",
    "In contrast, the use of post-tests was analyzed."
